<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="as-adv">as <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əz/    美 /əz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>同样地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ten years ago the population of our village was twice as large as that of theirs.
十年前我们村子的人口数量是他们的两倍。</p><footer>2008 陕西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some scientists even say we can live as long as 130 years!
一些科学家甚至说我们能活到130岁！</p><footer>2015 广东</footer></div>

<p>注: 否定句中也可用so代替as。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A friend is not so soon gotten as lost.
交友慢，失友快。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Maybe things are not as / so bad as they seem to be.
也许事情并不像看上去那么糟。</p><footer>2019 全国改</footer></div></div>